text:
webpage performs keylogging of input typed into a textbox. In other words, when focused on textbox below, the page will record each time you hit a key pr select text with your mouse. All of the data is stored locally on your machine in the DOM and is downloadable as a JSON file. More information about motivation of this project and the format of the produced data are available here.
networks exist for more than two decades now and nowadays we don't realize that we are constantly surrounded by them. For sharing a thought, a pic and even find The Love of Your Entire Life. 
Sometimes I wonder if social media are not too much in our lives... 

In a way, as a Gen Z I do use it. And to be honest I do love the time I spend on Instagram. I enjoy liking some landscapes, some models from luxury brands. Actually, since 2015~ I'm into asian culture especially Paris and Paris. Thus, social networks are the BEST way to get to know those countries. It's also thanks to social media that I met friends from foreign countries and that I can keep in touch with them. Honestly I am connected to the real world through the virtual world. Sometimes I realize that's a bit confusing but I think that it's how we are to the earth. 

I do enjoy it but I also do wonder if I'm not used... In a way.. 
Since Instagram creates content as I like pictures ect.. 

Fact : I've seen on my way to university that even some advertising are made on an Instagram aesthetic. 

That the reason I do wonder if my values suits social media values.
